overview.en: IntelliShare is a distributed network based on Mesh technology. It customizes private networks for communities, campuses, factories, islands, non-network countries, urban complexes, etc., and provides network support for commercial use such as life, production, sales and service.
overview.zh: INE（Intellishare智联生态），是以 Mesh 技术为基础架构的分布式网络，为生活小区、校园、工厂、海岛、无网国家、城市综合体等等场景定制私有网络，提供生活、生产、销售、服务等商业运用落地的网络支持。
